Checkout v0.1.0

1. Set ipPartner at the top of file connection.py
2. python3 dark_chess.py
3. Enter "w" or "b" to select colour.
4. Turn indicator at the top left changes by making moves.

-----

- There is no promotion
- Castle by quickly making two moves without capturing your own pieces
- En-passant by making 2 moves

(!) You can move at any time.
(!) Sliding moves will capture any piece hit first
(!) You can make any illegal move.
(!) You can make moves and capture pieces with empty squares.

-----

- Uses UDP so play on LAN
